00:16:56.480 --> 00:17:01.989
China. It's like living here is like smoking
three packs of cigarettes every day. This

00:17:01.989 --> 00:17:07.220
is the real problem in the world. And this
pollution, it's not only creates health problems,

00:17:07.220 --> 00:17:12.220
but the darkness of the pollution means that
it's absorbing sunlight and heating the air

00:17:12.220 --> 00:17:17.400
and this is why these pollutant particles,
the dark ones, are the second leading cause

00:17:17.400 --> 00:17:22.559
of global warming after carbon dioxide. The
black carbon and brown carbon in these particles.

00:17:22.559 --> 00:17:27.230
And they also cause health impacts. And they're
also very short lived. So if you control them,

00:17:27.230 --> 00:17:31.690
they're actually a very fast method of slowing
global warming. In fact if, they're the only

00:17:31.690 --> 00:17:34.860
method, by controlling those particles is
