00:17:34.860 --> 00:17:40.299
sea ice, because they're short lived. Along
with methane which is number three in terms

00:17:40.299 --> 00:17:45.740
of the leading causes of global warming. And
by the way methane, the main source of methane,

00:17:45.740 --> 00:17:52.950
well one of the main sources, is from natural
gas mining. And this is a big issue because

00:17:52.950 --> 00:17:59.950
the short lived impact of that methane over
the 20 year time frame is 80 times more significant

00:17:59.950 --> 00:18:03.720
per unit mass than carbon dioxide. 80 to 100
times.

