00:20:12.860 --> 00:20:21.110
as well, simultaneously reducing water pollution,
were wind, and concentrated solar power, geothermal

00:20:21.110 --> 00:20:27.929
power, tidal power, wave power, solar photovoltaics,
hydroelectric power. And that's for electric

00:20:27.929 --> 00:20:33.750
power. For transportation it's using these
electricity sources to power battery electric

00:20:33.750 --> 00:20:38.700
vehicles. And in some cases hydrogen fuel
cell vehicles. And the reason battery electrics

00:20:38.700 --> 00:20:43.240
are so good is that they're four to five times
more efficient than internal combustion. So

00:20:43.240 --> 00:20:51.330
