00:46:45.820 --> 00:46:53.400
output for the next 30 years 'cause these
things last. And that resulting number is

00:46:53.400 --> 00:46:58.020
your per kilowatt hour cost. And if that number
compares favorably with the number that you

00:46:58.020 --> 00:47:03.640
